text: Queens Eyot Clubhouse Queens Eyot from downstream) Queen's Eyot is an island in the River Thames in England on the reach above Boveney Lock, just upstream of Oakley Court near Windsor, Berkshire. The island is owned by Eton College and contains a club house that is available for hire for functions. ==See also== *Islands in the River Thames ==External links== *Queens Eyot Category:Islands of Berkshire Category:Islands of the River Thames Category:Bray, Berkshire
title: Queen's Eyot
